5. Find Most Frequent Element
Problem Given a list of integers, return the most frequent element. If there are ties, return any one.
Example
[1,1,2,3,3,3,4] → 3
What Netflix is testing
* Frequency counting
* Simple optimization
* Clear intent
Strong signals
* One-pass count, second-pass max
* Mention alternative (heap / sort) but choose simplest
* Tests: single element, negative numbers, ties
